Nguva dzose dzandaizoona munhu wa Mwari kuburikidza ne Emmanuel TV mumba -

0:32:39.260,0:32:44.400
Ndaipedza usiku ndichiona ne kunamata nemunhu wa Mwari, Senior Prophet T.B. Joshua.

0:32:44.400,0:32:47.920
