0:32:47.920,0:32:53.120
Ndakasarudza kuuya nokuti musiyano pakati pomunhu wa Mwari nevamwe vanhu vose,

0:32:53.120,0:32:55.020
avo vakanga vachiedza kundinunura munguva yakapfuura,

0:32:55.020,0:32:59.900
ndeyekuti munhu wa Mwari anozvininipisa zvikuru uye akarereuka.

0:32:59.900,0:33:05.720
Ane mwoyo kune vanhu uye rudo rwechokwadi kuvanhu.

